FIGS. 1 to 11 are simplified cross-sectional views illustrating successive steps of fabrication of an embodiment of an N-channel MOS transistor, of a P-channel MOS transistor, and of an NPN-type bipolar transistor;


FIG. 12 is an enlarged view of an NPN-type bipolar transistor obtained by the method illustrated in FIGS. 1 to 11; and


FIGS. 13 to 17 show steps of fabrication of an alternative bipolar transistor of NPN type according to the present invention.
